    {
      "id": "1CdKSrIEXOi0InwwopRvz",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3852.8416651583993,
      "y": 281.5460720033002,
      "width": 1078.041748046875,
      "height": 180,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1A",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1753471347,
      "version": 144,
      "versionNonce": 1450231347,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1773696836362,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Each test contains multiple test cases. The first line contains the number of test cases t(1≤t≤500). The description of the test cases \nfollows.\n\nThe first line of each test case contains an integer n(1≤n≤100), denoting the size of the board.\n\nThe following n lines contain n integers each; the j-th integer on the i-th line is ai,j(1≤ai,j≤n2), denoting the color of candies on the \nboard.\n\nIt is guaranteed that the sum of n over all test cases does not exceed 500.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Each test contains multiple test cases. The first line contains the number of test cases t(1≤t≤500). The description of the test cases \nfollows.\n\nThe first line of each test case contains an integer n(1≤n≤100), denoting the size of the board.\n\nThe following n lines contain n integers each; the j-th integer on the i-th line is ai,j(1≤ai,j≤n2), denoting the color of candies on the \nboard.\n\nIt is guaranteed that the sum of n over all test cases does not exceed 500.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Gd6z_xjgrGRSa0auA7603",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3852.4076385247313,
      "y": 479.85178615131224,
      "width": 49.19993591308594,
      "height": 18.4,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1B",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 246282931,
      "version": 235,
      "versionNonce": 445393533,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773696836362,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Output",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 7,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Output",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.15
    },
    {
      "id": "U4E-02HXEKhG-HZ8ORWs0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3848.972839513535,
      "y": 510.02636118118426,
      "width": 1027.87109375,
      "height": 80,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1C",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1112183741,
      "version": 237,
      "versionNonce": 1132431315,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773696836362,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "For each test case, print \"YES\" if a valid rearrangement exists, and \"NO\" otherwise.\n\nYou can output the answer in any case (upper or lower). For example, the strings \"yEs\", \"yes\", \"Yes\", and \"YES\" will be recognized as \npositive responses.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "For each test case, print \"YES\" if a valid rearrangement exists, and \"NO\" otherwise.\n\nYou can output the answer in any case (upper or lower). For example, the strings \"yEs\", \"yes\", \"Yes\", and \"YES\" will be recognized as \npositive responses.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
