      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1773696836362,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "In the first test case, no row or column consists of all candies with the same color; the board can be left as it is.\n\nIn the second test case, the first row consists of all candies of color 1h. The board can be rearranged by swapping a1,1 with a2,1. After the \nrearrangement, the board becomes",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In the first test case, no row or column consists of all candies with the same color; the board can be left as it is.\n\nIn the second test case, the first row consists of all candies of color 1h. The board can be rearranged by swapping a1,1 with a2,1. After the \nrearrangement, the board becomes",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
